column2: select top # S.ObjID, S.z, &&&, L1.ew, L1.ewErr, L1.continuum &&&, L2.ew, L2.ewErr, L2.continuum FROM SpecPhoto AS S JOIN SpecLine AS L1 ON S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID WHERE (specclass=# or specclass=#) and L1.LineId = # and L2.LineId = # and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
